title: Which song is it that has a female lead singer saying 'yeah, yeah, *yeah*, yeah' possibly twice? It seems to be a pop song and fairly well known. - Quora

response.answer_text: The one that comes to mind for me is the song “Young Blood” by The Naked and Famous.
Possibly “Your Daddy don’t Know” (What your Momma’s going to do tonight) By estimable Canadian Rock Band, Toronto.
